üß™ Testing Your Setup
After installation, run these commands to verify everything works:

bash

Copy

Download
# Check installation
kursarscript --version

# Run the test script
kursarscript examples/virtual_economy.kspl

# Start interactive mode
kursarscript -i

# Test VR environment (if installed)
kursarscript -v examples/vr_demo.kspl
üîÑ Upgrading
bash

Copy

Download
# Upgrade to latest version
pip install --upgrade kursarscript

# Upgrade specific components
pip install --upgrade kursarscript-vr
‚ùì Troubleshooting
Common Issues
"Command not found"

bash

Copy

Download
# Add Python Scripts to PATH (Windows)
setx PATH "%PATH%;C:\Python38\Scripts"

# Or use Python module directly
python -m kursarscript.cli --version
Permission Errors

bash

Copy

Download
# Use user installation
pip install --user kursarscript
Missing Dependencies

bash

Copy

Download
# Install with upgrade flag
pip install --upgrade --force-reinstall kursarscript
Getting Help
Check GitHub Issues

Join Discord Community

Email: support@kursarscript.dev

